header.gameNote: AARON'S AMERICAN ATHLETIC CONFERENCE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Rob Gray somehow manages to find room between three defenders to find an open Galen Robinson Jr. underneath the rim for a layup.
videos.headline: Houston's Gray finds daylight for assist

videos.description: B.J. Taylor penetrates to the rim and feeds A.J. Davis for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: UCF's Davis goes baseline for dunk

videos.description: B.J. Taylor gets the ball knocked away but it falls into Chad Brown's hands for an emphatic slam.
videos.headline: UCF's Brown right place, right time for dunk

videos.description: Rob Gray grabs the loose ball and races up the court to lay in a tough basket between defenders.
videos.headline: Houston's Gay goes coast-to-coast for tough layup

videos.description: Rob Gray somehow gets a shot up and off the glass between three defenders for an and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Houston's Gray flexes muscles after layup
